## Description {#details}

This class can be derived from and used by targets to hold private target-specific information for each <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module">Module</a>.

Objects of type are accessed/created with <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/machinemoduleinfo/#a92d88d2c22a932066d294be13e2baf55">MachineModuleInfo::getObjFileInfo</a> and destroyed when the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/machinemoduleinfo">MachineModuleInfo</a> is destroyed.

Definition at line 56 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/machinemoduleinfo-h">MachineModuleInfo.h</a>.
